oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Discussion - Chasin' That Neon Rainbow: The Rise of Alan Jackson - 2015-04-11
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Panel discussion on the career rise of Alan Jackson from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on April 11, 2015. Participants include record company executives Tim Dubois and Mike Dungan, along with songwriter Jim McBride, Jackson band members Danny Groah and Roger Wills. Presented in support of the exhibit Alan Jackson: 25 Years of Keepin’ It Country.
